# Third-party licenses

Nova Protocol's compiled binaries statically link the Rust crates listed below.
Their licenses require the license text to travel with the distribution, so this
file ships in every build (web `dist/credits/` and the native bundle).

This file is GENERATED by `cargo-about` from `about.toml` + `about.hbs` - do not
edit by hand. It is produced fresh at build/release time (and locally via
`scripts/gen-licenses.sh`), so it always matches the dependency graph it ships
with.

